Prep time took awhile, but it was delish! I just need to make it a habit of doing prep stuff on weekends i.e. having chopped onions, bell pepper, & other veggies on hand so I don't have to mess with it during the week. I took the advice of one of the other cooks & broiled the salmon before hand. I was afraid if I didn't the salmon wouldn't have been cooked enough. The whole family liked it, even the baby!

